    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "學生透過課堂上的英語聽和說活動，將提高英語的聽和說能力。學生將改善發音，且有能力將語言應用於日常情境，並使用到學生直接感興趣的主題中。要求學生在所有課堂活動中以及準備課堂中使用的報告，演示文稿和角色扮演時都使用英語。",
        "en": "Students will develop listening and speaking ability in English, using English listening and speaking activities in class. Students will improve pronunciation, will identify and use language for everyday contexts, and will identify and apply language for topics of immediate interest to students. Students will be expected to use English in all class activities and in preparing reports, presentations, and role plays for use in class."
    },
